a:18:{s:4:"name";s:6:"Bentyl";s:11:"small_descr";s:79:"Bentyl (Dicyclomine) is used for treating symptoms of irritable bowel syndrome.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:57:"Bentyl wird zur Behandlung von Reizdarmsyndrom verwendet.";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:103:"Bentyl est utilisé pour le traitement de l'intestin fonctionnel / du syndrome de l'intestin irritable.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:99:"Bentyl es utilizado para el tratamiento del intestino funcional / síndrome de intestino irritable.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:101:"Bentyle si usa per il trattamento  del intestino funzionale/della sindrome dell'intestino irritabile.";s:10:"full_descr";s:4909:"<p><strong>Drug Uses</strong><br /><br />Bentyl is used for treating symptoms of irritable bowel syndrome. It may also be used for other conditions determined by your doctor.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>How to use</strong><br /><br />Use Bentyl as directed by your doctor. Check the label on the medicine for exact dosing instructions.&nbsp;<br /> Bentyl is usually given as an injection at your doctors office, hospital, or clinic. If you will be using Bentyl at home, a health care provider will teach you how to use it. Be sure you understand how to use Bentyl . Follow the procedures you are taught when you use a dose. Contact your health care provider if you have any questions. <br /> Bentyl is for intramuscular (IM) injection only. It is NOT for intravenous (IV) use. <br /><br /><strong>Drug Class and Mechanism</strong><br /><br />Bentyl is an anticholinergic. It works by blocking a chemical in the smooth muscle of the stomach and intestines, causing them to relax, which reduces cramping.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Missed Dose</strong><br /><br />If you miss a dose of Bentyl , take it as soon as possible. If it is almost time for your next dose, skip the missed dose and go back to your regular dosing schedule. Do not take 2 doses at once.&nbsp;<br />Storage<br /><br />Store Bentyl at room temperature between 68 and 77 degrees F (20 and 25 degrees C) in a tightly closed container. Brief periods at temperatures of 59 to 86 degrees F (15 to 30 degrees C) are permitted. Store away from heat, moisture, and light. Do not store in the bathroom. Keep Bentyl out of the reach of children and away from pets.</p><p><strong>Warnings/Precautions</strong><br /><br />Do not use Bentyl if:&nbsp;<br /> you are allergic to any ingredient in Bentyl; <br /> you have blockage of the esophagus, stomach, intestine, or urinary tract; <br /> you have heart problems due to severe bleeding; <br /> you have glaucoma; <br /> you have inflammation of the esophagus due to acid reflux, loss of strength in the intestinal muscles, or chronic inflammation and ulceration of the bowel; <br /> you have myasthenia gravis (a condition in which the muscles become progressively paralyzed); <br /> you are breast-feeding. <br /> Some medical conditions may interact with Bentyl . Tell your doctor or pharmacist if you have any medical conditions, especially if any of the following apply to you: <br /> if you are pregnant, planning to become pregnant, or are breast-feeding <br /> if you are taking any prescription or nonprescription medicine, herbal preparation, or dietary supplement <br /> if you have allergies to medicines, foods, or other substances <br /> if you have chronic inflammation or ulcers of the bowel, diarrhea, enlargement of the prostrate, hiatal hernia, kidney or liver disease, a nervous system disease, overactive thyroid, or urinary blockage or retention <br /> if you have heart disease, heart failure, a history of rapid heartbeat, or high blood pressure. <br /> Some MEDICINES MAY INTERACT with Bentyl . Tell your health care provider if you are taking any other medicines, especially any of the following: <br /> Amantadine, antiarrhythmics (eg, quinidine), antihistamines (eg, diphenhydramine), benzodiazepines (eg, diazepam), monoamine oxidase inhibitors (MAOIs) (eg, phenelzine), narcotic pain medicine (eg, meperidine), nitrates (eg, nitroglycerin, isosorbide), nitrites (eg, sodium nitrite), phenothiazines (eg, chlorpromazine), sympathomimetics (eg, pseudoephedrine), or tricyclic antidepressants (eg, amitriptyline) because they may increase the risk of Bentyl 's side effects <br /> Metoclopramide or phenothiazines (eg, chlorpromazine) because their effectiveness may be decreased by Bentyl.<br />Digoxin because the risk of its side effects may be increased by Bentyl.</p><p><strong>Possible Side Effects</strong><br /><br />Check with your doctor if any of these most common side effects persist or become bothersome:&nbsp;<br /> blurred vision; constipation; decreased sweating; difficulty sleeping; dizziness; drowsiness; dry mouth; headache; lightheadedness; loss of taste; nausea; nervousness. <br /> Seek medical attention right away if any of these severe side effects occur: <br /><br /> Severe allergic reactions (rash; hives; itching; difficulty breathing; tightness in the chest; swelling of the mouth, face, lips, or tongue); agitation; confusion; diarrhea; difficulty focusing your eyes; difficulty moving; difficulty speaking; difficulty urinating; disorientation; exaggerated sense of well-being; fainting; hallucinations; pounding in the chest; rapid heartbeat; short-term memory loss; unusual weakness; vomiting. <br /><br /><strong>More Information</strong><br /><br />Bentyl is to be used only by the patient for whom it is prescribed. Do not share it with other people.<br /> If your symptoms do not improve or if they become worse, check with your doctor.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:17582:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Bentyl</span> <span class="hps">est utilis&eacute; pour traiter</span> <span class="hps">les sympt&ocirc;mes du syndrome</span> <span class="hps">du c&ocirc;lon irritable</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Bentyl</span> <span class="hps">est un anticholinergique</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Il bloque</span> <span class="hps">une substance chimique dans</span> <span class="hps">le muscle lisse</span> <span class="hps">de l'estomac</span> <span class="hps">et des intestins,</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> ce qui</span> <span class="hps">les d&eacute;tend et</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; son tour,</span> <span class="hps">r&eacute;duit</span> <span class="hps">les crampes.</span></span></p><p><strong>A</strong><strong>DMINISTRATION</strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Utilisez</span> <span class="hps">Bentyl</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">selon les instructions de votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin.</span></span></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ne prenez pas</span> <span class="hps">Bentyl</span> <span class="hps">en plus grandes quantit&eacute;s</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou plus longtemps</span> <span class="hps">que recommand&eacute; par votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Prenez</span> <span class="hps">Bentyl</span> <span class="hps">avec un</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">verre d'eau plein</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Si vous</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">manquez une dose</span> <span class="hps">Bentyl</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">prenez-la d&egrave;s</span> <span class="hps">que possible</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Si</span> <span class="hps">c'est presque le temps</span> <span class="hps">pour votre</span> <span class="hps">dose suivante, sautez</span> <span class="hps">la dose oubli&eacute;e et</span> <span class="hps">reprenez votre</span> <span class="hps">programme de dosage r&eacute;gulier</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Ne prenez pas 2</span> <span class="hps">doses &agrave; la fois</span><span>.</span></span></li></ul><p><strong>CONSERVATION</strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Gardez Bentyl</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; la temp&eacute;rature ambiante</span><span class="alt-edited">, au-dessous de</span> <span class="hps">86 degr&eacute;s</span> <span class="hps">F (30 degr&eacute;s</span> <span class="hps">C</span><span>)</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Ne le gelez pas. </span></span><br /><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> </span></span>Entreposez  loin de la chaleur et l'humidit&eacute;. Ne conservez pas dans la salle de   bain. Gardez <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Bentyl</span> </span>hors de la port&eacute;e des enfants et loin des animaux.</p><p><strong>INFORMATION ADDITIVE:</strong><br /><br />L'ingr&eacute;dient actif: Dicyclomine hydrochloride.</p><p><strong>RENSEIGNEMENTS DE S&Eacute;CURIT&Eacute;</strong></p><p><strong>N'utilisez pas Bentyl:</strong></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous &ecirc;tes allergique</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; un ingr&eacute;dient de Bentyl</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous avez</span> <span class="hps">le blocage</span> <span class="hps">de l'&oelig;sophage</span><span>, de l'estomac</span><span>, de l'intestin</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps">des voies urinaires</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous</span> <span class="hps">avez des probl&egrave;mes cardiaques</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">en raison d'</span> <span class="hps">une h&eacute;morragie s&eacute;v&egrave;re</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">vous avez le glaucome</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous avez une inflammation</span> <span class="hps">de l'&oelig;sophage</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">en raison d'</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">un reflux acide</span><span>, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>la perte</span> <span class="hps">de force dans les</span> <span class="hps">muscles de l'intestin</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">ou une inflammation chronique</span> <span class="hps">et une ulc&eacute;ration</span> <span class="hps">de l'intestin</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous avez</span> <span class="hps">la myasth&eacute;nie grave</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>une maladie dans laquelle</span> <span class="hps">les muscles deviennent</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">progressivement paralys&eacute;s</span><span>)</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous</span> <span class="hps">allaitez</span><span>.</span></span></li></ul><p>Contactez votre m&eacute;decin imm&eacute;diatement si l'un de ces cas s'applique &agrave; vous.</p><p>Certaines  conditions m&eacute;dicales peuvent interagir avec Bentyl. Informez votre  m&eacute;decin ou votre pharmacien si vous avez des conditions  m&eacute;dicales,  surtout si une des conditions suivantes s'applique &agrave; vous:</p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Amantadine</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps atn">les antiarythmiques (</span><span>par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, quinidine</span><span>), les antihistaminiques</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>par exemple, diphenhydramine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps atn">les benzodiaz&eacute;pines (</span><span>par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, diaz&eacute;pam</span><span>)</span><span>, les inhibiteurs</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">de monoamine oxydase</span> <span class="hps">(IMAO</span><span class="atn">) (</span><span>par exemple, ph&eacute;nelzine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">les </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">m&eacute;dicaments contre la douleur</span> <span class="hps">narcotiques</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, m&eacute;p&eacute;ridine</span><span>)</span><span class="atn">, les nitrates (</span><span>par exemple nitroglyc&eacute;rine,</span> <span class="hps">isosorbide</span><span>), les nitrites</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span>, le nitrite</span> <span class="hps">de sodium</span><span>), les ph&eacute;nothiazines</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, chlorpromazine</span><span>)</span><span class="atn">, les </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="atn">sympathomim&eacute;tiques (</span><span>par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, pseudo&eacute;ph&eacute;drine)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps atn">les antid&eacute;presseurs tricycliques (</span><span>par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, amitriptyline</span><span>), parce</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">qu'ils peuvent augmenter le</span> <span class="hps">risque d'effets secondaires</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">Bentyl</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Metoclopramide</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou les ph&eacute;nothiazines</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, chlorpromazine</span><span>), car leur</span> <span class="hps">efficacit&eacute; peut &ecirc;tre diminu&eacute;e</span> <span class="hps">par</span> <span class="hps">Bentyl</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Digoxine</span> <span class="hps">parce que le risque</span> <span class="hps">de ses effets secondaires</span> <span class="hps">peut &ecirc;tre augment&eacute; par</span> <span class="hps">Bentyl</span><span>.</span></span></li></ul><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Ce n'est pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">une liste compl&egrave;te</span> <span class="hps">de toutes les interactions</span> <span class=